fullConversation.content: Hey! I'm CORA, and I'm going to help you see exactly how much profit you're leaving on the table. Takes about 3 minutes. First - what should I call you?
john
Great to meet you, John! What type of construction work do you do? [business_types]
Plumbing, Remodeling, Concrete, Painting and Framing
How long have you been in business? [years_in_business]
Industry Veteran
And how would you describe your business size? [business_sizes]
Growing Company
Where do you primarily work? [service_areas]
Regional
Who are your typical customers? [customer_types]
Homeowners and Businesses
How do you currently track your expenses and jobs? [tracking_methods]
Paper & Folders, Spreadsheets and QuickBooks
What's your biggest challenge with the business side? [pain_points]
Can't track profits, Paperwork chaos, Missing tax deductions, No time for books and Cash flow issues
When's your busiest time of year? [busy_seasons]
Summer
What's your main goal for the next year? [business_goals]
Increase Profits
Excellent! I've got a great picture of your business. Your personalized dashboard is ready. Remember, the more data you add, the smarter I get. Ready to dive in? [complete_onboarding]
